---
title: Gyoza-Inspired Pork Noodles with Cabbage and Sesame Seeds
description: Delight in the savoury charm of this stir-fry! Tender pork, inspired by gyoza flavours, tossed with chow mein noodles and vibrant veggies. Finished with toasted sesame seeds for a nutty crunch, it's a quick and satisfying dish that brings the essence of your favourite dumplings to life.
